profile:
NORTHERN SPIRIT PLUMBING & HEATING Inc.
Northern Spirit Plumbing and Heating prides ourselves in delivering absolute peace of mind as we believe your property matters. We have been providing exceptional customer satisfaction throughout the Fraser Valley and Lower Mainland. We use highly specialized equipment such as HEPA vacuums to ensure no harmful dust particles or construction debris are released into the air. In an era of environmental crisis Northern Spirit Plumbing and Heating delivers best practices in this area.  If you want to have absolute peace of mind where we value honesty and integrity, give us a call.
Monday-Friday 8 am till 5 pm normal rates after 5 pm and all day Sunday/ Holidays overtime rates apply.

profile:
At Vedder Residential we specialize in providing professional, informative, no pressure service every time we step into your home. We work with you to determine the right repair or replacement, and then get that work done in a timely and professional manner.

Vedder Residential is based out of Chilliwack and offers a wide range of plumbing services from unclogging sinks, well filtration systems, faucet repair and full house re-pipes.
 
Installations of Plumbing Fixtures & Appliances
Partial or Whole Home Repipes
Full Drain Cleaning Services
Faucet, Tub & Shower Repairs
Toilet Repair and Replacement
Unclogging Toilets
Tub & Shower Installs
Relocating Fixtures
Installing Laundry Tubs
Installing Outdoor Hosebibs
Performing Leak Searches & Repair
Well Pumps
Well Pressure Tanks
Well Filtration
Plumbing Inspections
Insurance Reports

We install, repair and maintain a variety of heating equipment from furnaces and boilers, to water heaters and fireplaces.
 
Furnace Repair, Tune-Ups & Installations

Boiler Replacements

BBQ Boxes

If you are looking for additional comfort indoors we install, repair and maintain air conditioners, heat pumps and indoor air quality(IAQ) products.

products: Vedder Residential supplies and installs a variety of products from plumbing fixtures such as Toilets, Faucets, Tubs & Showers. As well as Furnaces, Boilers, Tank and Tankless Water Heaters, Air Conditioners, Heat Pumps, Well Pumps and Pressure Tanks.
services: We deal in annual maintenance, repair and replacement of your home's plumbing, heating and air conditioning systems. We provide Free Quotes on system replacement and offer extended emergency service.
brands:
We repair and service all makes of fixture and appliance.
We install only reputable and reliable equipment from manufacturers such as Rheem, Delta, Toto and American Standard.
specialities: Our specialty is a well rounded, customer oriented service. We provide photo documentation of all repairs and replacement. We run thorough tests on your home's mechanical systems to ensure everything is running smoothly now and in the future. Pricing is provided completely upfront with a variety of options to fit any budget.
payment_method: Cash, Certified Cheque, Interac, Visa, Mastercard
